# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# combined — __bool__, __str__, __repr__ across all 5 pathlib subjects
#
# 5 classes x 3 methods = 15 rows.
# All values are false; pathlib defines no bool, string, or repr
# conversion operators in its class __dict__s. Path objects are filesystem
# path abstractions; these conversion protocols are not part of the path
# interface as defined in each class's own __dict__.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

